Get ESPN's WNBA player box data

Source: R/espn_wnba_data.R
espn_wnba_player_box.Rd

Get ESPN's WNBA player box data

espn_wnba_player_box(game_id)

Arguments

game_id

Game ID

Value

Returns a player boxscore data frame

Author

Saiem Gilani

Examples

# \donttest{
  try(espn_wnba_player_box(game_id = 401244185))
